data.eml:eml: Cephalodella ungulata n. sp. (Monogononta: Notommatidae), a new rotifer species from North-West Germany, with notes on C. tenuiseta (Burn, 1890)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Fischer, Claus, Ahlrichs, Wilko H. (2006): Cephalodella ungulata n. sp. (Monogononta: Notommatidae), a new rotifer species from North-West Germany, with notes on C. tenuiseta (Burn, 1890). Zootaxa 1378: 49-59, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175031
